ðŸ•’ Digital Clock App
A sleek, responsive digital clock built with React, featuring real-time updates and a minimalist design. This project showcases dynamic time rendering using JavaScript's Date object and React hooks like useState and useEffect.
> Features
- Displays current time in 24-hour format with AM/PM
- Styled with Google Fonts and a custom background image

> Tech Stack
- React (Functional Components + Hooks)
- CSS (Custom styling + Google Fonts)
- JavaScript (Date object for time logic)
